The paper deals with techniques for improving the performance of cellular networks using massive MIMO, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of several CS sub-disciplines. However, the main focus of the paper is on signal processing and optimization techniques for wireless communication systems, which suggests that the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SI (Signal Processing), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
